
Ranger Help for: claim
======================

SYNTAX:      claim
USAGE:       Any terrain
SLOT COST:   15
BASE SP:     250 sp(one time use)
SKILL TYPE:  aid

SUMMARY:
This skill is a one time use only skill. It allows a Ranger to set his
or her range. A Ranger's range is where he or she feels at home, a place
they always come back to. If a Ranger has a place that they explore in
often, or like..they might should set it as their range. Any Ranger
exploring in their range, will get bonuses in all aplicable skills and
in fighting. Such as, a Ranger fighting it out in his or her range might
do extra damage with Gaeia's help, and knowing the terrain..gains an
advantage in a fight over his or her opponent. Ranges are aproximately
the size of a realm(wizard's area).

